### Task 7: Use Bootstrap to Build a Website
Explanation:
Create a simple site (e.g., event page or restaurant menu) using Bootstrap 5. It should
include:
• Navbar, content area, card layout, and footer
Focus on: Using Bootstrap classes instead of custom CSS.


